headline: Benjamin Heselton Joins Lamb Weston as Chief Information Officer
summary: EAGLE, Idaho, May 07, 2025--Lamb Weston Holdings, Inc. (NYSE: LW) announced that Benjamin (Ben) Heselton has joined the company as its chief information officer.
